Content: My name is Jay! I love programming, and I have a passion for simulation games. When I'm not developing my own person projects, I work as a freelance web designer. I'm hoping people will enjoy my games, and that I will continue posting new projects as time goes on! Thank you for taking an interest in me, please feel free to let me know what you think of my current game <em><strong>LifeSim</strong></em>! I have a lot of interesting ideas I plan on implementing, but I would love feedback to help me along the way! :D;